data.description: Welcome to this absolutely stunning private piece of paradise nestled on 2.25 acres in the coveted area of Webster! This prestigious brick & stucco residence exudes elegance & charm. A private & extensive concrete driveway beckons you towards the inviting natural wood staircase & open foyer adorned w/marble tile floors. An open kitchen w/granite counters & SS appliances is accompanied by a convenient 1st-floor laundry. Gleaming hardwoods grace the entire house, leading to 5 spacious bdrms & 3.5 impressively tiled baths. Grandeur continues w/an elegant living room, dining room & a welcoming family room featuring a wood-burning fireplace. Finished basement offers a sauna, showers & bath. An awe-inspiring panoramic room awaits, bathing in natural light filtering through sliding doors & skylights w/an indoor-inground gunite pool w/hot tub seamlessly connecting to a spacious patio w/built-in grill & counters! A private fenced area w/hot & cold water adds practicality to this already perfect picture. This exceptional property effortlessly blends serenity & luxury for the buyer seeking an extraordinary lifestyle. Welcome home to your own piece of paradise!
